Usage: reportGateCount [-help] [-hinst <hinst>] [-level <level>]
                       [-limit <gateCount>] [-outfile <fileName>] [-stdCellOnly]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-hinst <hinst>          # name of hinst (string, optional)
-level <level>          # level of hierarch (int, optional)
-limit <gateCount>      # minimum number of gate count (int, optional)
-outfile <fileName>     # file name (string, optional)
-stdCellOnly            # For standard cell only (bool, optional)